(40, 'Birchley 4 Seater Sofa', 72055.00, 89, 'Birchley-Soft-Chenille-4-Seater-Sofa-Ice.jpg', 'Birchley-Soft-Chenille-4-Seater-Sofa-Ice-Angle1.jpg', 'Birchley-Soft-Chenille-Ice-Angle2.jpg', 'Birchley-Soft-Chenille-Ice-Angle3.jpg', 'Ice-Swatch-Angle4.jpg', 'Birchley-Soft-Chenille-4-Seater-Sofa-Ice-Hover.jpg', 4, 'Sofas & Armchair', 16, 'Sofas & Couches', 'The Birchley 4-Seater Sofa is a fully assembled, made-to-order piece designed for larger living spaces, featuring a grand, expansive size with clean lines and a contemporary silhouette; built for supreme comfort and durability with a robust hardwood frame, it boasts generous removable foam seat cushions, fiber-filled back cushions, and matching scatter cushions, all upholstered in a velvety soft chenille fabric available in many sophisticated colors, and is finished with light wooden block feet that add a touch of natural warmth and elegance.', '98x296x92', '', '', 'Chenille Polyester Fabric', '', '', 'Linen', 'Mink', 'Heather', 'Birchley-Soft-Chenille-4-Seater-Sofa-Linen.jpg', 'Birchley-Soft-Chenille-4-Seater-Sofa-Mink.jpg', 'Birchley-Soft-Chenille-4-Seater-Sofa-Heather.jpg', '2025-11-11 11:28:41'),
(41, 'Flower Vase Cylinder', 240.00, 255, 'FLOWER_VASE_CYLINDER.png', 'FLOWER_VASE_CYLINDER_Angle1.png', 'FLOWER_VASE_CYLINDER_Angle2.png', 'FLOWER_VASE_CYLINDER_Angle3.png', 'FLOWER_VASE_CYLINDER_Angle4.png', 'FLOWER_VASE_CYLINDER_Hover.jpg', 5, 'Home Decorations', 22, 'Vases, Planters & Greenery', 'This versatile and beautifully crafted clear glass cylinder vase is an essential piece for any home or event, perfect for showcasing floral arrangements, decorative fillers, or pillar candles.\r\n\r\nCrafted from quality glass, this vase is designed for both beauty and practicality, providing a stable base and ample height for a variety of decorative purposes.', '9 x 9 x 20', '', '', 'Glass', '', '', 'Clear', '', '', 'FLOWER_VASE_CYLINDER_Clear.png', '', '', '2025-11-11 11:33:38'),
(42, 'Sword Grass in Cement Pot', 719.00, 200, 'SWORD_GRASS_IN_CEMENT_POT.png', 'SWORD_GRASS_IN_CEMENT_POT_Angle1.png', 'SWORD_GRASS_IN_CEMENT_POT_Angle2.png', 'SWORD_GRASS_IN_CEMENT_POT_Angle3.png', 'SWORD_GRASS_IN_CEMENT_POT_Angle4.png', 'SWORD_GRASS_IN_CEMENT_POT_Hover.png', 5, 'Home Decorations', 22, 'Vases, Planters & Greenery', 'Bring a touch of maintenance-free greenery into your space with this charming artificial Sword Grass plant. The realistic foliage features spiky leaves in vibrant shades of green and subtle rustic orange/brown tips. The plant is set in a small, stylish white cement pot with an attractive black marble-like veining pattern, finished with small decorative pebbles around the base. This compact, decorative piece is perfect for desks, shelves, or small accent tables, instantly adding texture and color without the need for watering.', '16x16x23', '', '', 'Polyethylene Cement', '', '', 'White', '', '', 'SWORD_GRASS_IN_CEMENT_POT_White.png', '', '', '2025-11-11 11:43:16'),
(45, 'Glass Vase CS-6', 249.00, 255, 'GLASS_VASE_CS-6.png', 'GLASS_VASE_CS-6_Angle1.png', 'GLASS_VASE_CS-6_Angle2.png', 'GLASS_VASE_CS-6_Angle3.png', 'GLASS_VASE_CS-6_Angle4.png', 'GLASS_VASE_CS-6_Hover.png', 5, 'Home Decorations', 22, 'Vases, Planters & Greenery', 'This is a classic clear glass bubble bowl identified as the GLASS VASE CS-6. It features a smooth, continuous spherical body with a slight flattening at the base for stability. The clear, colorless soda glass is completely transparent, ensuring that any contentsâ€”whether they be vibrant flower stems, floating candles, or a small terrariumâ€”are fully visible and enhanced by the light. The wide, circular rim offers easy access for arranging and cleaning, making this a highly functional and versatile low-profile vase.', '15 x 15 x 12', '', '', 'Soda Glass', '', '', 'Clear Glass', '', '', 'GLASS_VASE_CS-6_Clear_Glass.png', '', '', '2025-11-12 05:03:12'),
(46, 'Seagrass Natural Urn Shaped Basket', 2634.00, 230, 'Seagrass_Natural_Urn_Shaped_Basket.png', 'Seagrass_Natural_Urn_Shaped_Basket_Angle1.jpg', 'Seagrass_Natural_Urn_Shaped_Basket_Angle2.jpg', 'Seagrass_Natural_Urn_Shaped_Basket_Angle3.png', 'Seagrass_Natural_Urn_Shaped_Basket_Angle4.png', 'Seagrass_Natural_Urn_Shaped_Basket_Hover.png', 5, 'Home Decorations', 22, 'Vases, Planters & Greenery', ' architectural interest to your home with this elegantly shaped 36cm urn basket, featuring a distinctive silhouette that transforms everyday storage into a decorative statement. The fine seagrass weaving creates beautiful texture whilst the graceful proportions make it perfect for displaying dried flowers or storing household essentials with natural sophistication.\r\n\r\nCrafted in India using traditional techniques, this stunning basket brings warmth and organic appeal to any area of your home.\r\n\r\nWhether styled as a plant holder, used for storing blankets, or simply displayed as a decorative accent, its timeless urn shape and natural materials create lasting beauty that enhances both modern and traditional interiors.', '33 x 36 x 36', '', '', 'Seagrass', '', '', 'Walnut Wood Dye', '', '', 'Seagrass_Natural_Urn_Shaped_Basket_Walnut_Wood_Dye.png', '', '', '2025-11-12 05:19:54'),
(47, 'White Orchid in Pot', 4613.00, 255, 'White_Orchid_in_Pot.png', 'White_Orchid_in_Pot_Angle1.png', 'White_Orchid_in_Pot_Angle2.png', 'White_Orchid_in_Pot_Angle3.png', 'White_Orchid_in_Pot_Angle4.png', 'White_Orchid_in_Pot_Hover.png', 5, 'Home Decorations', 22, 'Vases, Planters & Greenery', 'Experience the timeless beauty of pristine white orchids with these exquisite arrangements, available in both tall and medium heights to suit any space perfectly. The elegant ceramic pots and perfectly formed blooms create stunning focal points in dining kitchens, living rooms, and entrance halls, with the medium size ideal for tables and the tall version perfect for floor displays.\r\n\r\nEnjoy the prestige and beauty of exotic orchids without the delicate care requirements that real orchids demand. These expertly crafted pieces deliver continuous blooming beauty that enhances any interior with sophisticated floral elegance, making every day feel special whilst offering the perfect size for your specific styling needs.', '115 x 35 x 35', '', '', 'Ceramic', 'Cement ', 'Plastic', 'White', '', '', 'White_Orchid_in_Pot_White.png', '', '', '2025-11-12 05:27:42'),
(48, 'Roswell Stain Resistant Shaggy Rug', 10469.00, 255, 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug.png', 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug_Angle1.png', 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug_Angle2.png', 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug_Angle3.png', 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug_Angle4.png', 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug_Hover.png', 5, 'Home Decorations', 24, 'Rugs & Floor Coverings', 'These rugs are meticulously crafted using machine-made techniques, ensuring precision and consistency. The four-metre wide looms, computer-aided design program, and skilled handwork guarantee impeccable binding, carving, and trimming, adding a final touch of perfection.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re looking to add warmth and cosiness or elevate your living room\'s style, the Roswell Stain Resistant Shaggy Rug is an excellent choice. Experience luxurious comfort and durability while enhancing the overall aesthetic of your space.\r\n', '80 x 150', '120 x 170', '160 x 230', 'Polypropylene Fabric', '', '', 'Dark Blue', 'Dark Grey', 'Jewel Green', 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug_Dark_Blue.png', 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug_Dark_Grey.png', 'Roswell_Stain_Resistant_Shaggy_Rug_Jewel_Green.png', '2025-11-12 05:36:37');
