(53, 'Zelah Oak Mirror', 10081.00, 255, 'Zelah_Oak_Mirror.png', 'Zelah_Oak_Mirror_Angle1.png', 'Zelah_Oak_Mirror_Angle2.png', 'Zelah_Oak_Mirror_Angle3.png', 'Zelah_Oak_Mirror_Angle4.png', 'Zelah_Oak_Mirror_Hover.png', 5, 'Home Decorations', 21, 'Wall Décor & Mirrors', 'This Zelah Oak mirror is handmade from high quality oak and designed to compliment the rustic Zelah oak. A beautiful addition to any bedroom or guest room, it adds a touch of rustic charm to the room.\r\n\r\nThe Zelah collection features a broad range of chunky, rustic oak furniture all finished in a warm honey oak. Our craftsmen carefully distress the furniture before using a special process to enhance the natural features of the wood grain. Manufactured from sustainably sourced American White Oak which has a waxed finish, this collection is rapidly becoming a customer favourite.', '89 x 120 x 2', '', '', 'Solid Oak ', 'Manufactured Veneered Oak ', 'Glass', 'Oak', '', '', 'Zelah_Oak_Mirror_Oak.png', '', '', '2025-11-12 06:08:07'),
(54, 'Hanging Mirror Luco R40', 1499.00, 255, 'HANGING_MIRROR_LUCO_R40.png', 'HANGING_MIRROR_LUCO_R40_Angle1.png', 'HANGING_MIRROR_LUCO_R40_Angle2.png', 'HANGING_MIRROR_LUCO_R40_Angle3.png', 'HANGING_MIRROR_LUCO_R40_Angle4.jpg', 'HANGING_MIRROR_LUCO_R40_Hover.png', 5, 'Home Decorations', 21, 'Wall Décor & Mirrors', 'The HANGING MIRROR LUCO R40 is a striking, circular wall accent defined by its beautiful and luminous mosaic frame. The frame is intricately decorated with shining pieces of seashell (Mother-of-Pearl), interspersed with metallic silver tiles that catch and reflect light, lending a sophisticated coastal or glam aesthetic to any room. Measuring 40cm in diameter, this mirror features a shatterproof finishing and comes ready to hang with an included string, though users should ensure they check the wall\'s strength and use appropriate mounting hooks.', '40 x 1.4 x 40', '', '', 'Medium Density Fibreboard', 'Sea Shell', 'Glass', 'White', '', '', 'HANGING_MIRROR_LUCO_R40_White.png', '', '', '2025-11-12 06:25:13'),
(56, 'Hanging Mirror Arbre Round NA D36', 679.00, 255, 'HANGING_MIRROR_ARBRE_ROUND_NA_D36.png', 'HANGING_MIRROR_ARBRE_ROUND_NA_D36_Angle1.png', 'HANGING_MIRROR_ARBRE_ROUND_NA_D36_Angle2.png', 'HANGING_MIRROR_ARBRE_ROUND_NA_D36_Angle3.png', 'HANGING_MIRROR_ARBRE_ROUND_NA_D36_Angle4.jpg', 'HANGING_MIRROR_ARBRE_ROUND_NA_D36_Hover.png', 5, 'Home Decorations', 21, 'Wall Décor & Mirrors', 'The HANGING MIRROR ARBRE ROUND NA D36 features a clean, simple design perfect for Scandinavian, Japandi, or Modern Farmhouse aesthetics. It consists of a circular mirror encased in a smooth, thick frame made of light-toned wood, likely stained with a subtle \"Walnut Wood Dye\" to enhance the visible, natural grain. The frame\'s wide, uniform thickness provides a contemporary border to the reflective surface, making it an understated yet elegant piece ideal for an entryway, bedroom, or living area.', '36 X 0.9 x 36', '', '', 'Medium-Density Fibreboard', '', '', 'Walnut Wood Dye', '', '', 'HANGING_MIRROR_ARBRE_ROUND_NA_D36_Walnut_Wood_Dye.png', '', '', '2025-11-12 06:39:48'),
