(60, 'Laila Natural Organic Tall Ceramic Table', 4628.00, 255, 'Laila_Natural_Organic_Tall_Ceramic_Table_Lamp.png', 'Laila_Natural_Organic_Tall_Ceramic_Table_Lamp_Angle1.png', 'Laila_Natural_Organic_Tall_Ceramic_Table_Lamp_Angle2.png', 'Laila_Natural_Organic_Tall_Ceramic_Table_Lamp_Angle3.png', 'Laila_Natural_Organic_Tall_Ceramic_Table_Lamp_Angle4.png', 'Laila_Natural_Organic_Tall_Ceramic_Table_Lamp.png', 6, 'Light Fixtures', 28, 'Table & Desk Lamps', 'The Laila Natural Organic Tall Ceramic Table Lamp is a quirky and stylish lighting option that makes a bold statement in any space. Its neutral ceramic base, with a subtle speckled texture, is paired with a self-lined linen shade, creating an eye-catching and balanced design. This lamp is perfect for Scandi or coastal interiors, offering a relaxed yet contemporary feel that enhances any room.\r\nMade from high-quality ceramic and linen, the Laila lamp complements various interior styles with its timeless design and neutral tones. Its unique look makes it a versatile accent piece, ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, or office spaces. Whether you\'re looking to add a touch of elegance to a minimalist setting or a warm, natural vibe to a more eclectic design, this lamp effortlessly blends into any dÃ©cor.', '56 x 20 x 33', '', '', 'Ceramic ', 'Linen', '', 'Beige', '', '', 'Laila_Natural_Organic_Tall_Ceramic_Table_Lamp_Beige.png', '', '', '2025-11-12 08:36:29'),
