(99, 'Talland 2 Door 2 Drawer Wardrobe', 26552.00, 156, 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Product-Image.jpeg', 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Angle-1.jpeg', 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Angle-2.jpeg', 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Angle-3.jpeg', 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Angle-4.jpeg', 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Product-Image-Hover.jpeg', 1, '', 5, '', 'The Talland 2 Door 2 Drawer Wardrobe offers a perfect blend of modern practicality and timeless style, expertly made to order and fully assembled in the UK. Crafted from durable, scratch-resistant vinyl, this wardrobe is designed to maintain its fresh, polished look for years to come. Available in clean white, grey, or taupe finishes with a contrasting wooden top, it brings a light and spacious feel to any interior. The distinctive panel design and textured finish enhance its rustic charm, while the two drawers with linen-effect lined interiors glide smoothly on metal runners for effortless use. Inside, a hanging rail provides ample space for clothes, combining practicality with understated elegance.', '182.5x74x53', '', '', 'Scratch-Resistant Vinyl Finish', 'Manufactured Wood Frame', 'Contrasting Wooden Top', 'White', 'Gray', 'Taupe', 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Color-White.jpeg', 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Color-Gray.jpeg', 'Talland-White-2-Door-2-Drawer-Wardrobe-Color-Taupe.jpeg', '2025-11-12 20:14:49'),
